    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1890-03-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1890-03-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="296" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d296">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Snowden</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-03-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 21,
                            1890</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 30.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The protocol explanatory of the scope and
                        effect of article <hi rend="smallcaps">i</hi> of the treaty between the
                        United States of America and Greece of December 10–22, 1837, which
                        accompanied your dispatch No. 28 of the 4th ultimo, has been received. The
                        Department has approved the protocol in question and printed the same for
                        the information of the public.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">James G. Blaine.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
